content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 427.6 - Effect of national register eligibility determination on state register eligibility

State Regulations

Properties which have not been nominated by the
commissioner for listing on the National Register, but which have been
determined eligible for such listing by the Department of the Interior of the

United States shall also be deemed eligible for listing on the State Register
and may be nominated thereto in accordance with this Part. Notes
